  ],
  "remarks": "Ksenia Mishonova is a Children’s Rights Ombudsman of the Moscow Oblast. She is involved in the illegal deportation of Ukrainian children to the territory of the Russian Federation. She also facilitated the transfer of custody of Ukrainian children in Russia, and the granting of Russian citizenship to them. Her actions infringe Ukraine’s law and administrative order, and violate the rights of Ukrainian children.",
